Hummin
======

Command line client for the Public Domain Books Library (http://publicdomainbook.net/).

= Install =

apt-get install tor libreadline-dev libncurses5-dev
go get github.com/gobs/cmd github.com/hailiang/gosocks github.com/ttacon/chalk code.google.com/p/gcfg

= Config =

cat ~/.humminrc

[Global]
downloads = ~/ebooks
lang = en
num = 20

= Preferred language =

If you want to override the preferred language selection in your .hummirc,
you can specify `lang:any` in your query.

